### Subscription Plan Requests
# Base URL: http://localhost:3000

### Admin login (required before creating plans)
POST http://localhost:3000/admin/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "admin_username",
  "password": "admin_password"
}

# Use the returned admin `_id` as the `adminid` header for protected routes.
# Example: adminid: 6432abcd1234ef567890

# Create 1-month plan
POST http://localhost:3000/plans
Content-Type: application/json
adminid: <ADMIN_ID>

{
  "name": "1 Month Plan",
  "duration_days": 30,
  "price": 100,
  "planType": "base",
  "is_active": true,
  "features": [
    "Access to all vendor listings",
    "Priority customer support",
    "Basic booking analytics"
  ]
}

