### Get active plans
GET http://localhost:3000/plans

### Create add-on plan
POST http://localhost:3000/plans
Content-Type: application/json
adminid: <ADMIN_ID>

{
  "name": "Featured Listing Add-on",
  "duration_days": 15,
  "price": 50,
  "planType": "addon",
  "is_active": true,
  "features": [
    "Featured placement",
    "Homepage visibility boost"
  ]
}

### Vendor purchases base subscription
POST http://localhost:3000/subscription/purchase
Content-Type: application/json
vendorid: <VENDOR_ID>

{
  "planId": "<BASE_PLAN_ID>"
}

### Vendor purchases add-on subscription
POST http://localhost:3000/subscription/add-on
Content-Type: application/json
vendorid: <VENDOR_ID>

{
  "planId": "<ADDON_PLAN_ID>",
  "startDate": "2026-05-04",
  "endDate": "2026-05-19"
}

### Admin assigns base subscription with explicit dates
POST http://localhost:3000/subscription/admin/assign
Content-Type: application/json
adminid: <ADMIN_ID>

{
  "vendorId": "<VENDOR_ID>",
  "planId": "<BASE_PLAN_ID>",
  "startDate": "2026-05-04",
  "endDate": "2026-06-03"
}

### Admin adds add-on to vendor subscription
POST http://localhost:3000/subscription/admin/add-on
Content-Type: application/json
adminid: <ADMIN_ID>

{
  "vendorId": "<VENDOR_ID>",
  "planId": "<ADDON_PLAN_ID>",
  "startDate": "2026-05-04",
  "endDate": "2026-05-19"
}

### Admin gets complete subscription data
GET http://localhost:3000/subscription/all
adminid: <ADMIN_ID>

### Admin gets 15-day expiration warnings
GET http://localhost:3000/subscription/expiring-soon
adminid: <ADMIN_ID>
